# ============================================================================
# _percli — zsh completion for **percli** — perses/perses, the
#            **CNCF Sandbox observability dashboarding platform** —
#            the cloud-native open-source successor to Grafana for
#            Kubernetes-native deployments, designed as **GitOps-
#            first** (every dashboard is a typed YAML or Cuelang DAC
#            artifact stored in git, applied to the Perses API
#            server via `percli apply -f`, never authored through a
#            click-through GUI as the primary source of truth).
#            Backed by Prometheus + Thanos + Cortex + Mimir + Loki +
#            Tempo + Jaeger + ClickHouse + InfluxDB + Pyroscope +
#            OpenTelemetry as data sources.  OIDC SSO via the
#            zitadel/oidc canonical Go OIDC library (against
#            Keycloak / Authentik / Auth0 / Okta / Microsoft Entra
#            ID / Google Workspace / GitHub OIDC / Cloudflare Access
#            / any RFC 6749 + OIDC 1.0 IdP).  Go=179 leader bump
#            continuing Axis 124 (OAuth 2.0 / OpenID Connect 1.0 /
#            IETF RFC 6749 + RFC 8252 + RFC 7636 PKCE + OIDC
#            Discovery + OIDC Dynamic Client Registration identity
#            protocol) at 2/0/0 via the canonical Go OIDC library
#            **github.com/zitadel/oidc/v3**.
# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
#   Repository : https://github.com/perses/perses
#                  (workspace member: cmd/percli/)
#   Maintainer : CNCF Sandbox project (graduated 2023);  lead
#                 maintainers: Augustin Husson, Antoine Thébaud,
#                 Augustin Husson from RedHat + Amadeus + Grafana
#                 Labs + GitLab + Google;  the original Perses
#                 project was donated to the CNCF by RedHat in
#                 2023 alongside its sister CNCF Sandbox project
#                 Korrel8r (observability-data correlation
#                 engine) and the Coral library (the typed
#                 dashboard schema layer)
#   License    : Apache-2.0
#   Stars      : 2,195
#   Language   : Go  (spf13/cobra for the CLI surface +
#                 zitadel/oidc/v3 for OIDC admin SSO +
#                 sigs.k8s.io/yaml for dashboard YAML
#                 unmarshalling + cuelang for typed Dashboards-
#                 as-Code (DAC) authoring + sirupsen/logrus for
#                 structured logging + perses-go-sdk for the
#                 typed Perses API client + a custom JSON Schema
